### Drop a course
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/enrollments/64d2f1bc9a7a4e001e9a1c33

###

### Get all enrollments for a student
GET http://localhost:3000/api/enrollments/student/64d2f1bc9a7a4e001e9a1a11

